{
  "stem": "13981.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he had-- he wanted to make sure he'd die.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I didn't ask how Eva Braun died, but the troops actually killed her or she committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then the troops doused their bodies with gasoline.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Russians were supposed to have picked up-- I mean, denied it for a long time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they had picked up the bodies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the reason they could identify the burned bodies, the Americans, later on, because they had dental x-rays of Hitler's.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they matched the skull x-rays with the x-rays they had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wouldn't know what to change.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I lived a happy and full and a very complete life, a wonderful family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Was lucky.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe one thing I could-- would try to do-- I didn't have a chance while I was younger-- to go to college.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I barely finished high school in 1964, at night classes, when I had already my family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that may be the only thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I am happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would like to tell those people who look in or see this or see the evidence to be aware that racial and religious strife is one of the worst things that can happen to humanity.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we see it right now in Yugoslavia and have seen it in many other parts of the world since.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You're welcome.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
